[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering Spring Boot configuration**\n\nI'm thinking about whether we should prefer certain annotations in Spring Boot, particularly spring-boot-autoconfigure. It seems like a more direct approach might help us avoid potential issues with SpringApplication. But now I’m wondering: does AnnotationConfigApplicationContext automatically include ConfigurationPropertiesBindingPostProcessor? I recall that @EnableConfigurationProperties is what registers them. There could be some concerns with condition report classes, so it might be worth editing that aspect!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0898fde1534ab2a6016a0bdb04f54c8194b89f47dbb8c95c52\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqC9sR1qgVW6euhAl9sVTCfuk8TUgzCBZs-1jE2aknn8Teq6BKCho-t_fiXj4DPzB4V4jdViTezEX1KVYnrimyyOsCKD3jeVKSn0BOL0yhJr19mrkLl-MTcd66BfzYPBta2vGIP6mQLUKjqvuInWrsUW-Qugs3OH9aGj3Z3Bh6VK3NLM8dlKLickaUhviutopS5dSdPWJ3kRafk-4G_aGfQC1Jxy47cMn_ld0VGDg9fcT5RQRS3pQgojqU9XzP9Ta5ckRqU-kIsvIAV3dbTBx5CySi56muqV7KWLQfffOQPP_abPeS6WDhPeT7jPO1ja4nIrVT_509-ZGTnnioKX02g2w6CBYQTA4Gwzf59x6zA8uPeOS0La9ujkaMT79fyCDa8K8w8tJzmhpjUC-Sq7B8vd8O6jWP1twEXTSPhEuvQTTtQfxcSmMYqF6JdHtwn0SW0sMkB5igRugevKoaq8W5CWYl3Mc4cR9WiWgdBoBjXB-9NEWmDv6waeB43HNZNRO4KFtKaRxjdNnidppjWbBZ_8em7SyLv_SfYk1EDESBj2qEvRRvCK2XKMF-qbscozB2GAkw4HEXj3tb0naqZ_Wh98ONQdtFRWm4sEfkoW6zEcR7R4Q1563jll2pOF1eyvt3uYoZBiItGapac0ECE2HK4c7ySbZCgturNm7-SUF0VvQJ8dQeVvwC9p1ISil92mPPabEJFbsLawc_dWNjWKn2OAoMYMgIC_fhHOfuhsHJA_f7G8AhWDVyJ9pwcUhKfLMpfZb7ti3Dtnqjpt3DLLEvwWRJpArhGE1C-4sjr3-RcMFxt9X6U8VUH-ggofKpk9rWRKjdTQ4mkCUcGWSNcUSv-glVMwoXFuom0ArA8esLsg-MUYBenYPeZvt0U2rVxLDczLNzJ6BJaFQnenTeWbRQmEVxy9Uv6kT21VuZO3vn0Ql-eKcXQPR0YcVvIN9-fX7O9Sh0iCrCHz4Rvasb9zcKVIRF6Nw3oz78FmTlyVw1tXAqpZHrZ14iYQ8C72fijG4mv3CAWU4sTCHoL_LioG4pirDuTGJQA4j1tBY2RA5PAO_90aB-ISUZCbEhZNBKcjFx98AlAePNg0PaWqbd1RARhgnm4uOHEy7G0dUSYuXR9_MmY6uIvs5Ro7qRv6Kd46CwU5PtxNHPsS-wKB5YeuQ1i_m6r1iXr